*Students, Research Assistant & Postdoc (招生与博士后)*\n
I am always looking for outstanding young talents to join my research group.
- Currently I've been actively advising graduate students at Tsinghua SIGS. Please check out the graduates' program for Electrical Engineering [https://www.sigs.tsinghua.edu.cn/en/2020/0916/c1668a20601/page.htm master] (SIGS) (2025 fall) and [https://www.sigs.tsinghua.edu.cn/en/1492/list.htm Ph.D] (2025 fall, only for International Students [./files/2025_Tsinghua_SIGS_Application_Guidelines_For_Int_Students.pdf (Application GUIDELINES)] now, living expenses are covered by SIGS scholarship).
- Several Post-Doc Positions are available. The salary package is Negotiable, but definitely >= ￥420k per year (pre-tax) including subsids from Shenzhen Goverment.
- Some Research Assistant(RA) positions are also available. We'll provide living expenses for qualified candidates.
- Visiting Scholars from other universities are also welcome.

Please send your CV to me if interested.
